This paper is likely to belong to the Information Theory (cs.IT) sub-category as it deals with error correction codes and decoding algorithms. It may also belong to the sub-categories of Architecture (cs.AR) and Embedded Systems (cs.ET) as it proposes an efficient hardware architecture for the encoder and decoder. Additionally, it may be relevant to the Data Structures (cs.DS) sub-category as it involves partial sums computations, and the Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-category as it deals with improving the performance of a system.
